<quiz>
  <question type="stack">
    <name>
      <text>Evaluating a numerical square using a quadratic identity</text>
    </name>
    <questiontext format="moodle_auto_format">
      <text><![CDATA[<p>
Evaluate the following expression using a quadratic identity:
\[
({@n@} + {@k@})^2
\]
</p>

<p>[[input:ans1]] [[validation:ans1]] [[feedback:prt1]]</p>]]></text>
    </questiontext>
    <generalfeedback format="moodle_auto_format">
      <text><![CDATA[<h3>Worked Solution</h3>

<p>
We use the identity:
</p>

<p>
\[
(a+b)^2 = a^2 + 2ab + b^2
\]
</p>

<p>
Let:
</p>

<p>
\[
a = {@n@}, \quad b = {@k@}
\]
</p>

<p>
Substitute into the identity:
</p>

<p>
\[
({@n@} + {@k@})^2 =
{@n@}^2 + 2({@n@})({@k@}) + {@k@}^2
\]
</p>

<p>
\[
= {@n^2@} + {@2*n*k@} + {@k^2@}
\]
</p>

<p>
\[
= {@correct@}
\]
</p>]]></text>
    </generalfeedback>
